 name=\"ISA\" />\n\n== Governance ==\nThe operation of the ISA is in the hands of the ISA Committee and is lay down within a set of rules.\n\n=== ISA Committee<ref name=\"ISACommittee\" /> ===\n1 January 2019 - 31 December 2019\n{| class=\"wikitable\" border=\"1\"\n|-\n|style=\"vertical-align:top\"|'''Honorable President'''\n* {{flagicon|NOR}} [[Harald V of Norway]]\n'''Honorable Members'''\n* {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Felipe VI of Spain]]\n* {{flagicon|GRE}} [[Constantine II of Greece]]\n{{Collapsible list\n  |framestyle  = border:none; padding:0;\n  | title      = Life Members&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  | bullets    = on\n  | 1          = {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Barry Hayes]]\n  | 2          = {{flagicon|DEN}} [[Eggert Benzon]]\n  | 3          = {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Dinny Reed]]\n  | 4          = {{flagicon|GBR}} [[Hamish Loudon]]\n  | 5          = {{flagicon|GER}} [[Karl Haist]]\n  | 6          = {{flagicon|HUN}} [[Gy\u00f6rgy Wossala]]\n  | 7          = {{flagicon|SUI}} [[Jean-Pierre Marmier]]\n  | 8          = {{flagicon|USA}} [[Rose Hoeksema]]\n}}  \n|style=\"vertical-align:top\"|'''Executive Committee'''\n* President {{flagicon|GER}} [[Michael Dietzel]]\n* Vice-presidents: \n** {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Nelson Horn Ilha]]\n** {{flagicon|CAN}} [[Peter Hall (sailor)|Peter Hall]]\n** {{flagicon|NED}} [[Han van Veen]]\n{{Collapsible list\n  |framestyle  = border:none; padding:0;\n  | title      = Secretary&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  | bullets    = on\n  | 1          = {{flagicon|USA}} [[Matias Collins]]\n}}\n{{Collapsible list\n  |framestyle  = border:none; padding:0;\n  | title      = Treasurer&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  | bullets    = on\n  | 1          = {{flagicon|GER}} [[Susanne K\u00fcffer]]\n}}\n{{Collapsible list\n  |framestyle  = border:none; padding:0;\n  | title      = Communication Committee&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs