isleri, [http://www.fmo.org.tr www.fmo.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Metallurgical engineers\n|Metalurji m\u00fchendisleri\n|1970\n|<ref>metalurji.org.tr, [http://www.metalurji.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Meteorology engineers\n|Meteoroloji m\u00fchendisleri\n|1970\n|<ref>meteroroloji.org.tr, [http://www.meteroroloji.org.tr]{{dead link|date=July 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n|Geology engineers\n|Jeoloji m\u00fchendisleri\n|1974\n|<ref>jmo.org.tr, [http://www.jmo.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Interior architects\n|\u0130\u00e7 mimarlar\n|1976\n|<ref>icmimarlarodasi.org.tr, [http://www.icmimarlarodasi.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|[[The Chamber of Geophysical Engineers of Turkey|Geophysics engineers]]\n|Jeofizik m\u00fchendisleri\n|1986\n|<ref>jeofizik.org.tr, [http://www.jeofizik.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Environmental engineers\n|\u00c7evre m\u00fchendisleri\n|1992\n|<ref>cmo.org.tr, [http://www.cmo.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Textile engineers\n|Tekstil m\u00fchendisleri\n|1992\n|<ref>tmo.org.tr, [http://www.tmo.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Landscape architects\n|Peyzaj mimarlar\u0131\n|1994\n|<ref>peyzajmimoda.org.tr, [http://www.peyzajmimoda.org.tr]</ref>\n|-\n|Food engineers\n|G\u0131da m\u00fchendisleri\n|1996\n|<ref>gida.org.tr, [http://www.gida.org.tr]{{dead link|date=July 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Chamber of Computer Engineers of Turkey|Computer engineers]]\n|Bilgisayar m\u00fchendisleri\n|2012\n|<ref>bimo.org.tr, [http://www.bimo.org.tr]</ref>\n|}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n[[Category:1954 establishments in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Organizations based in Ankara]]\n[[Category:Engineering societies based in Turkey]]\n[[Category:Architecture-related professional associations|Turkish]]\n[[Category:Turkey-related lists]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox organization\n| name          = Union of Chambers of Turkish Engineers and Architects<br><small>T\u00fcrk M\u00fchendis ve Mimar Odalar\u0131 Birli\u011fi</small>\n| bgcolor       = <!-- header back